# Code Editor - KX Dashboards

Original URL: https://code.kx.com/dashboards/codeeditor/

# Code Editor

![User Editor](../img/codeeditor/codeeditor.jpg)

A text and code editor. Content can be assigned to [view state
parameters](../viewstateparameters/).

## Basics

![User Editor](../img/codeeditor/codeeditorbasics.png)

_Name_

    A name for the component provided by the user. 
_Language_

    Select from `json`, `plaintext`, `handlebars`, `html`, `java`, `javascript`, `markdown`, `python`, `r`, `sql`, `typescript`, `xml`, and `q`.
_Value_

    Assign content of editor to a [view state parameter](../viewstateparameters/).
_Debounce Update (ms)_

    Frequency of validity checks
_Format on Value Change_

    When checked, every change in the _Value_ will reformat the document if a formatter if available for the selected _Language_
_Show Toolbar_

    Display button shortcuts
    ![User Editor](../img/codeeditor/codeeditortoolbar.jpg)

## Editor Configuration

_Show Minimap_

    Display content map
    ![User Editor](../img/codeeditor/codeeditorminimap.jpg)
_Show Line Numbers_

    Display line numbers in left-hand column
_Read only_

    Prevent editing of content
    ![User Editor](../img/codeeditor/readonlyeditor.jpg)

## Style

[Style](../style/#component-style) for common settings

